{"id": "art-119", "label": "Art. 119", "title": "Art. 119", "slug": "art-119", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 119 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1722239908\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2308\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1722239908\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Consiliul de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>,\nrespectiv directoratul, convoac&#259; de îndat&#259; adunarea general&#259;, la\ncererea <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span> reprezentând, individual\nsau împreun&#259;, cel <span class=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span> 5% din capitalul\nsocial sau o cot&#259; mai mic&#259;, dac&#259; în actul constitutiv se prevede\nastfel <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> dac&#259; cererea cuprinde <span\nclass=SpellE>dispozi&#355;ii</span> ce intr&#259; în <span class=SpellE>atribu&#355;iile</span>\nadun&#259;rii.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_133582730\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2307\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_133582730\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Adunarea general&#259; va fi convocat&#259; în termen de\ncel mult 30 de zile <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> se va întruni în termen\nde cel mult 60 de zile de la data primirii cererii.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_445995151\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2306\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_445995151\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)În cazul în care consiliul de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>,\nrespectiv directoratul, nu convoac&#259; adunarea general&#259;, <span\nclass=SpellE>instan&#355;a</span> de la sediul <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>,\ncu citarea consiliului de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>,\nrespectiv a directoratului, va putea autoriza convocarea adun&#259;rii generale\nde c&#259;tre <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarii</span> care au formulat\ncererea. Prin <span class=SpellE>aceea&#351;i</span> încheiere <span\nclass=SpellE>instan&#355;a</span> aprob&#259; ordinea de zi, <span\nclass=SpellE>stabile&#351;te</span> data de <span class=SpellE>referin&#355;&#259;</span>\nprev&#259;zut&#259; la art. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>123 alin. (2)</span><span\nstyle='color:black'>, data <span class=SpellE>&#355;inerii</span> adun&#259;rii\ngenerale <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>, dintre <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionari</span>,\npersoana care o va prezida.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_794942491\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2305\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_794942491\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Costurile convoc&#259;rii adun&#259;rii generale, precum\n<span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> cheltuielile de judecat&#259;, dac&#259; <span\nclass=SpellE>instan&#355;a</span> aprob&#259; cererea conform alin. (3), sunt\nsuportate de societate.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}